          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript is a compendium and guide used for consultation by those wanting to learn the benefits (such as liberation at death) of visiting the pilgrimage center of Prayāga, and the rules and regulations (Hindu law, Dharma) that govern such visits. Text is part of a larger work called the "Bridge to the three holy cities" (Tristhalīsetu), which deals with three major pilgrimage centers in India: Kāśī (Varāṇasī), Prayāga (Allahabad), and Gayā.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
            <msItem>
              <title>Prayāgaprakaraṇa</title>
              <title type="vernacular">प्रयागप्रकरण</title>
