              </author>
              <colophon>Colophon: iti bhaṭṭarāmeśvarasūnubhaṭṭanārāyaṇaviracite tristhalīsetau prayāgaprakaraṇaṃ samāptaṃ // itaḥ paraṃkāśīprakaraṇaṃ bhaviṣyati // saṃvat 19104 (f. 47v).</colophon>
